# UI Design Reference

Reference mockups are in `.cursor/designs/`. Use them when building frontend components.

## 1. Piano Roll Editor (.cursor/designs/ui-mockup-piano-roll-editor.png)

Three-panel layout:

- **Left sidebar** (~220px, bg #1a1a2e): App logo "AMA-MIDI", "+ New Song" button, scrollable song list (title + note count per item, active item highlighted blue), user avatar + name + logout at bottom.
- **Main area** (flex-1, bg #0d1117): Top toolbar with editable song title, description, action buttons (Save, Share, Undo, Redo). Status bar showing track range, time range, note count, online users. Piano roll grid below.
- **Right panel** (~280px, bg #1a1a2e, conditional): Appears when a note is selected. "Edit Note" form: Title (text), Description (textarea), Track (dropdown 1-8), Time (number 0-300), Color (swatches). Update (blue) and Delete (red outline) buttons. History section showing ledger entries.

### Piano Roll Grid

- 8 columns labeled "Track 1" through "Track 8"
- Y-axis: time 0s-300s flowing downward, labels every 10s
- Background: #0d1117 with subtle grid lines (#1e293b)
- Notes: colored circles (~20px diameter) at (track, time) intersections
- Selected note: glowing ring highlight
- Click empty cell: snap-to-grid note placement
- Default colors: blue #3B82F6, red #EF4444, green #22C55E, purple #A855F7, yellow #EAB308

## 2. Song Dashboard (.cursor/designs/ui-mockup-song-dashboard.png)

- **Top nav**: Logo left, search bar center, notification + user avatar right
- **Page header**: "My Songs" title, subtitle, "+ Create New Song" button (blue)
- **Filter tabs**: All Songs | Shared with me | Recent. Sort dropdown on right.
- **Card grid** (3 columns, responsive): Each card (#1e293b, rounded) has mini piano roll preview thumbnail, song title (bold white), description (gray), bottom stats row (note count, collaborator count, last modified)

## 3. Login / Register (.cursor/designs/ui-mockup-login.png)

- Centered card (~400px, bg #1a1a2e) on dark background (#0a0a1a)
- Logo "AMA-MIDI" with music note icon, subtitle "Enterprise MIDI Editor & Collaboration Suite"
- Tab switcher: Sign In | Sign Up
- Sign In: email field, password field, "Forgot password?" link, blue "Sign In" button, divider, "Sign in with SSO" outline button
- Background: faint piano roll grid pattern at low opacity

